	<h1 class="title">让传统的材料有现代感，京都瓷器 Sfera 在伦敦办了个展</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/161922/small/161922.jpg?1442322894" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">廖婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-24 06:50:22 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/17961/medium/17961.jpg?1448281303" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


